f Allison KH, Hammond MEH, Dowsett M, et al.Estrogen and Progesterone Receptor Testing in Breast Cancer: ASCO/CAP Guideline Update.J Clin Oncol 2020;38:1346-1366; Arch Pathol Lab Med 2020;144:545-563.
